### Prototype creation with FIGMA

## Figma
Figma is a collaborative software for creating prototypes in the field of UX or UI design. 
It is mainly used as a web application. Figma also runs as a desktop app for MacOS and Windows 
and as a mobile app for Android and iOS. Figma designs can be built modularly and shared with 
others in real time.[1] The name Figma is derived from the English noun figment 
(figment of the imagination, illusion). Competing products are Adobe XD and Sketch.

## Professional Prototyping
With Figma, a professional prototyping is possible. Pitching the idea created in a
very conviceable and impressive way requires a professional prototype look.
